DEFINE
	VAR __DS0FilterTable = 
		TREATAS({"A",
			"B",
			"C",
			"D",
			"E",
			"F",
			"G"}, 'D_Batiment'[etiquette_dpe])

	VAR __DS0FilterTable2 = 
		TREATAS({2025}, 'LocalDateTable_5280315f-9dd4-4ec0-aaca-82264563f989'[Année])

	VAR __DS0FilterTable3 = 
		FILTER(
			KEEPFILTERS(VALUES('D_Localisation'[code_insee_ban])),
			OR(
				'D_Localisation'[code_insee_ban] = "30352",
				'D_Localisation'[code_insee_ban] = "25413"
			)
		)

	VAR __DS0Core = 
		SUMMARIZECOLUMNS(
			'D_Batiment'[etiquette_dpe],
			'D_Localisation'[code_postal_ban],
			__DS0FilterTable,
			__DS0FilterTable2,
			__DS0FilterTable3,
			"Countetiquette_dpe", CALCULATE(COUNTA('D_Batiment'[etiquette_dpe]))
		)

	VAR __DS0PrimaryWindowed = 
		TOPN(
			201,
			SUMMARIZE(__DS0Core, 'D_Batiment'[etiquette_dpe]),
			'D_Batiment'[etiquette_dpe],
			1
		)

	VAR __DS0SecondaryBase = 
		SUMMARIZE(__DS0Core, 'D_Localisation'[code_postal_ban])

	VAR __DS0Secondary = 
		TOPN(62, __DS0SecondaryBase, 'D_Localisation'[code_postal_ban], 1)

	VAR __DS0BodyLimited = 
		NATURALLEFTOUTERJOIN(
			__DS0PrimaryWindowed,
			SUBSTITUTEWITHINDEX(
				__DS0Core,
				"ColumnIndex",
				__DS0Secondary,
				'D_Localisation'[code_postal_ban],
				ASC
			)
		)

EVALUATE
	__DS0Secondary

ORDER BY
	'D_Localisation'[code_postal_ban]

EVALUATE
	__DS0BodyLimited

ORDER BY
	'D_Batiment'[etiquette_dpe], [ColumnIndex]

		TREATAS({"D"}, 'D_Batiment'[etiquette_dpe])

	VAR __DS0FilterTable2 = 
		TREATAS({"Gaz"}, 'D_Batiment'[type_energie_groupe])

	VAR __SQDS0FilterTable = 
		TREATAS({"D"}, 'D_Batiment'[etiquette_dpe])

	VAR __SQDS0Core = 
		SUMMARIZECOLUMNS(
			'D_Batiment'[type_energie_principale_chauffage],
			__SQDS0FilterTable,
			"Sumconso_5_usages_ef", CALCULATE(SUM('F_DPE'[conso_5 usages_ef]))
		)

	VAR __SQDS0BodyLimited = 
		TOPN(3, __SQDS0Core, [Sumconso_5_usages_ef], 0)

	VAR __DS0Core = 
		SUMMARIZECOLUMNS(
			'LocalDateTable_5280315f-9dd4-4ec0-aaca-82264563f989'[Mois],
			'LocalDateTable_5280315f-9dd4-4ec0-aaca-82264563f989'[NoMois],
			'LocalDateTable_5280315f-9dd4-4ec0-aaca-82264563f989'[Année],
			__DS0FilterTable,
			__DS0FilterTable2,
			__SQDS0BodyLimited,
			"Averageconso_5_usages_par_m2_ef", CALCULATE(AVERAGE('F_DPE'[conso_5 usages_par_m2_ef]))
		)

	VAR __DS0PrimaryWindowed = 
		TOPN(
			201,
			SUMMARIZE(
				__DS0Core,
				'LocalDateTable_5280315f-9dd4-4ec0-aaca-82264563f989'[Mois],
				'LocalDateTable_5280315f-9dd4-4ec0-aaca-82264563f989'[NoMois]
			),
			'LocalDateTable_5280315f-9dd4-4ec0-aaca-82264563f989'[NoMois],
			1,
			'LocalDateTable_5280315f-9dd4-4ec0-aaca-82264563f989'[Mois],
			1
		)

	VAR __DS0SecondaryBase = 
		SUMMARIZE(__DS0Core, 'LocalDateTable_5280315f-9dd4-4ec0-aaca-82264563f989'[Année])

	VAR __DS0Secondary = 
		TOPN(
			62,
			__DS0SecondaryBase,
			'LocalDateTable_5280315f-9dd4-4ec0-aaca-82264563f989'[Année],
			1
		)

	VAR __DS0BodyLimited = 
		NATURALLEFTOUTERJOIN(
			__DS0PrimaryWindowed,
			SUBSTITUTEWITHINDEX(
				__DS0Core,
				"ColumnIndex",
				__DS0Secondary,
				'LocalDateTable_5280315f-9dd4-4ec0-aaca-82264563f989'[Année],
				ASC
			)
		)

EVALUATE
	__DS0Secondary

ORDER BY
	'LocalDateTable_5280315f-9dd4-4ec0-aaca-82264563f989'[Année]

EVALUATE
	__DS0BodyLimited

ORDER BY
	'LocalDateTable_5280315f-9dd4-4ec0-aaca-82264563f989'[NoMois],
	'LocalDateTable_5280315f-9dd4-4ec0-aaca-82264563f989'[Mois],
	[ColumnIndex]
